DataSource.RecordSource:
DECLARE @text nvarchar(max)
Set @text = '?text';
IF @text!='' BEGIN
select Visitor_ID,Name,EmiratesID,Company,Nationality,Gender,Mobile,Email,Visitor_Image.Image as VisPicture from SecuLobby_VisitorInfo LEFT OUTER JOIN Visitor_Image ON dbo.SecuLobby_VisitorInfo.Visitor_ID = Visitor_Image.ID and[Type] = 1 WHERE ( Name LIKE '%' + @text + '%' OR EmiratesID LIKE '%' + @text + '%' OR Company LIKE '%' + @text + '%' OR Nationality LIKE '%' + @text + '%' OR Gender LIKE '%' + @text + '%' OR Mobile LIKE '%' + @text + '%' OR Email LIKE '%' + @text + '%') ORDER BY Name
END ELSE
begin select Visitor_ID,Name,EmiratesID,Company,Nationality,Gender,Mobile,Email,Visitor_Image.Image as VisPicture from SecuLobby_VisitorInfo LEFT OUTER JOIN Visitor_Image ON dbo.SecuLobby_VisitorInfo.Visitor_ID = Visitor_Image.ID and[Type] = 1 ORDER BY Name end
